575
00:24:38,289 --> 00:24:40,329
Check out this good-looking young man.

576
00:24:41,849 --> 00:24:42,569
Step aside.

577
00:24:42,730 --> 00:24:43,450
He's so weird.

578
00:24:43,490 --> 00:24:44,369
Maybe he's ill.

579
00:24:44,930 --> 00:24:46,569
Lu Buping, what are you doing?

580
00:24:47,769 --> 00:24:48,809
Father, why are you here?

581
00:24:48,849 --> 00:24:49,410
Look.

582
00:24:50,329 --> 00:24:51,410
So many fish.

583
00:24:51,609 --> 00:24:52,369
Are you drunk?

584
00:24:53,529 --> 00:24:55,730
No, I'm practicing martial arts.

585
00:24:57,210 --> 00:24:58,210
Monkey stealing peach.

586
00:24:59,289 --> 00:25:00,849
- S-Stop it.
- Earthshaking Palm.

587
00:25:03,250 --> 00:25:04,849
Mother, are you okay?

588
00:25:05,049 --> 00:25:06,129
Mr. Lu didn't mean it.

589
00:25:06,170 --> 00:25:07,849
He's poisoned by the mushrooms.

590
00:25:08,410 --> 00:25:11,129
Dear, I've been waiting for you
for a long time.

591
00:25:11,650 --> 00:25:13,129
It's been 500 years.

592
00:25:13,210 --> 00:25:14,569
Mr. Lu, what are you talking about?

593
00:25:14,569 --> 00:25:16,049
You said in your previous life

594
00:25:16,529 --> 00:25:18,170
that you wanted to
stay with me in this life.

595
00:25:19,129 --> 00:25:20,609
You wanted to have

596
00:25:21,369 --> 00:25:22,730
eleven fishes with me.

597
00:25:22,809 --> 00:25:24,049
No. Mother, I didn't say that.

598
00:25:24,129 --> 00:25:24,849
Take him inside now.

599
00:25:24,890 --> 00:25:26,129
Don't make a fool here.

600
00:25:26,170 --> 00:25:27,089
Mr. Lu. Mr. Lu.

601
00:25:27,089 --> 00:25:27,730
Let's go in.

602
00:25:27,769 --> 00:25:28,690
Take your medicine.

603
00:25:29,369 --> 00:25:30,089
Where are you going?

604
00:25:32,730 --> 00:25:33,650
I'll take you there.

605
00:25:34,170 --> 00:25:35,730
Let her off!

606
00:25:35,769 --> 00:25:36,650
I didn't say that.

607
00:25:40,250 --> 00:25:41,930
Go away. What are you looking at?

608
00:25:49,210 --> 00:25:50,490
What a pity to throw away

609
00:25:50,569 --> 00:25:51,730
these nice mushrooms.

610
00:25:51,809 --> 00:25:53,129
I worked hard to pick them.

611
00:25:57,329 --> 00:25:58,849
I had some and I was fine.

612
00:25:59,609 --> 00:26:01,369
I think Mr. Lu is too weak.

613
00:26:03,049 --> 00:26:04,210
Do I smell like alcohol?

614
00:26:04,529 --> 00:26:05,410
It's quite obvious.

615
00:26:05,410 --> 00:26:06,410
It's fine.

616
00:26:06,450 --> 00:26:07,210
Keling.

617
00:26:09,569 --> 00:26:10,569
Why are you here?

618
00:26:11,369 --> 00:26:12,410
I've recovered.

619
00:26:12,609 --> 00:26:14,410
I want to visit you and Mrs. Chun

620
00:26:14,650 --> 00:26:16,329
to thank you for taking care of me.

621
00:26:16,369 --> 00:26:17,170
No need.

622
00:26:17,250 --> 00:26:18,089
Go back.

623
00:26:18,410 --> 00:26:19,129
Boss.

624
00:26:19,129 --> 00:26:19,849
Why?

625
00:26:19,970 --> 00:26:21,569
Why what?

626
00:26:21,609 --> 00:26:23,089
We have different aspirations.

627
00:26:23,129 --> 00:26:24,809
I don't want anything to do

628
00:26:24,809 --> 00:26:25,849
with you officials.

629
00:26:27,129 --> 00:26:28,690
What's wrong with officials?

630
00:26:28,890 --> 00:26:30,849
Everything's wrong with officials.

631
00:26:30,890 --> 00:26:32,809
You are just like
your despicable brother.

632
00:26:32,930 --> 00:26:34,210
Boss, what are you doing?

633
00:26:34,289 --> 00:26:35,890
- Come on.
- Seriously.

634
00:26:35,930 --> 00:26:37,490
Anyway, don't come again.

635
00:26:39,569 --> 00:26:40,129
Boss.

636
00:26:40,650 --> 00:26:41,250
Boss.

637
00:26:42,769 --> 00:26:43,490
A-Si.

638
00:26:47,930 --> 00:26:50,369
You're still waiting here?

639
00:26:51,490 --> 00:26:53,049
Mr. Right is a no-show?

640
00:26:53,089 --> 00:26:54,890
You can't find me a date

641
00:26:54,930 --> 00:26:57,730
at the Marriage Bridge, either.

642
00:26:58,289 --> 00:26:59,210
Actually,

643
00:26:59,529 --> 00:27:02,490
I did find someone suitable for you.

644
00:27:03,210 --> 00:27:05,210
But I had diarrhea.

645
00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:07,609
The guy's mother was gone
once I went back.

646
00:27:08,529 --> 00:27:09,410
I don't know why,

647
00:27:09,450 --> 00:27:11,490
but I've been having diarrhea all day.

648
00:27:11,849 --> 00:27:14,529
I don't know when
preserved vegetables were made.

649
00:27:20,809 --> 00:27:21,289
Peilan.

650
00:27:21,369 --> 00:27:23,210
Mother, I think I'm poisoned.

651
00:27:24,010 --> 00:27:24,730
Mother.

652
00:27:24,970 --> 00:27:26,329
Sit down.

653
00:27:28,129 --> 00:27:28,849
Mother.

654
00:27:29,170 --> 00:27:31,210
Why didn't you tell me that Father came?

655
00:27:32,129 --> 00:27:34,129
Father.

656
00:27:34,809 --> 00:27:36,049
Why are you here?

657
00:27:36,089 --> 00:27:37,769
Father.

658
00:27:37,809 --> 00:27:39,690
When did you come?

659
00:27:40,529 --> 00:27:41,529
Father.

660
00:27:43,250 --> 00:27:44,730
Jinrong, don't move.

661
00:27:45,650 --> 00:27:46,890
Someone's sitting on your head.

662
00:27:47,250 --> 00:27:47,890
Wake up.

663
00:27:47,930 --> 00:27:48,650
Don't move, Jinrong.

664
00:27:48,690 --> 00:27:49,890
- Wake up.
- Don't move.

665
00:27:49,930 --> 00:27:51,170
Peilan, wake up.

666
00:27:53,089 --> 00:27:54,049
Peilan.

667
00:27:54,650 --> 00:27:55,450
Jinrong.

668
00:27:55,809 --> 00:27:57,490
Help!

669
00:28:03,250 --> 00:28:04,170
Does it still hurt?

670
00:28:06,369 --> 00:28:07,250
Mother.

671
00:28:07,730 --> 00:28:09,690
What if the Young Lord comes

672
00:28:09,690 --> 00:28:10,930
right now?

673
00:28:12,609 --> 00:28:13,369
Ruyu.

674
00:28:15,690 --> 00:28:16,730
How's Peilan?

675
00:28:16,890 --> 00:28:19,129
She's also poisoned by the mushrooms.

676
00:28:19,490 --> 00:28:21,170
Thankfully, it's only in the intestines

677
00:28:21,210 --> 00:28:22,490
and not in the blood.

678
00:28:22,529 --> 00:28:24,250
Neither has it hurt the organs.

679
00:28:25,569 --> 00:28:27,049
To put it simply, she's fine.

680
00:28:27,089 --> 00:28:27,769
Don't worry.

681
00:28:29,890 --> 00:28:32,250
I told Peilan
to throw away those mushrooms,

682
00:28:32,329 --> 00:28:33,450
but she just wouldn't.

683
00:28:33,490 --> 00:28:34,970
Master told her the same thing.

684
00:28:34,970 --> 00:28:35,809
Would she listen?

685
00:28:36,289 --> 00:28:38,569
Peilan is quite something.

686
00:28:38,650 --> 00:28:39,610
When will she ever

687
00:28:39,610 --> 00:28:41,809
change the habit
of keeping all the trash?

688
00:28:41,849 --> 00:28:43,890
Remember the day
she fed us leftover food

689
00:28:44,250 --> 00:28:46,250
from five days ago back in Qing City?

690
00:28:46,289 --> 00:28:47,450
We got food poisoning

691
00:28:47,490 --> 00:28:48,890
and almost reunited with Father.

692
00:28:48,890 --> 00:28:50,089
She almost died

693
00:28:50,129 --> 00:28:51,609
because of some mushrooms.

694
00:28:51,849 --> 00:28:53,650
We must teach her a lesson this time.

695
00:28:53,809 --> 00:28:55,089
You can't beat her up.

696
00:28:55,170 --> 00:28:56,410
She's still in a coma.

697
00:28:56,450 --> 00:28:57,450
Beat her up?

698
00:28:58,490 --> 00:28:59,730
She'd be lucky.

699
00:29:11,129 --> 00:29:12,369
Peilan.

700
00:29:13,930 --> 00:29:16,369
Peilan, you finally wake up.

701
00:29:17,890 --> 00:29:18,369
Mother.

702
00:29:18,369 --> 00:29:20,329
Lie down.

703
00:29:20,450 --> 00:29:21,170
Lie down.

704
00:29:23,250 --> 00:29:23,970
You...

705
00:29:25,329 --> 00:29:27,650
You want something to eat?

706
00:29:28,970 --> 00:29:30,849
Mother, I can't eat right now.

707
00:29:30,890 --> 00:29:33,490
Peilan, tell us what you want to eat.

708
00:29:36,250 --> 00:29:40,410
I'll get it for you even if I have to
climb a mountain of swords,

709
00:29:40,410 --> 00:29:42,849
or descend to the sea of fire.

710
00:29:44,650 --> 00:29:45,730
Yeah.

711
00:29:46,450 --> 00:29:47,809
Have whatever

712
00:29:48,170 --> 00:29:50,849
you'd like to have.

713
00:29:52,809 --> 00:29:56,849
Peilan, that mushroom
is highly poisonous.

714
00:29:58,250 --> 00:29:59,930
You'd be dizzy in the beginning.

715
00:30:00,210 --> 00:30:01,930
Then you'll start twitching

716
00:30:02,049 --> 00:30:03,210
and have hallucinations.

717
00:30:03,369 --> 00:30:05,369
Then you'll bleed
from all your orifices.

718
00:30:07,010 --> 00:30:09,650
Even Hua Tuo couldn't save you.

719
00:30:13,250 --> 00:30:15,250
I'm too incapable.

720
00:30:16,849 --> 00:30:19,369
Mother, am I dying?

721
00:30:21,490 --> 00:30:23,089
What about Mr. Lu?

722
00:30:24,329 --> 00:30:24,970
He...

723
00:30:29,129 --> 00:30:30,210
He's gone.

724
00:30:36,490 --> 00:30:37,609
He's gone?

725
00:30:42,410 --> 00:30:45,049
Mother, did we overdo it?

726
00:30:45,569 --> 00:30:46,650
Check on her.

727
00:30:50,490 --> 00:30:51,329
Is she fine?

728
00:30:52,250 --> 00:30:55,490
She's fine. Just weak.

729
00:30:55,529 --> 00:30:57,089
She'd better be fine, or you'll pay.

730
00:30:57,650 --> 00:30:58,450
It's your idea.

731
00:30:58,490 --> 00:31:00,250
What does it have to do with him?

732
00:31:05,809 --> 00:31:07,049
Unbelievable.

733
00:31:07,089 --> 00:31:09,609
This is unbelievable.

734
00:31:09,970 --> 00:31:12,690
When have I ever been treated like this?

735
00:31:12,769 --> 00:31:15,089
Young Lord, I've told you.

736
00:31:15,129 --> 00:31:17,210
We should teach that girl a lesson.

737
00:31:17,250 --> 00:31:17,809
I...

738
00:31:21,289 --> 00:31:22,529
You think I don't know?

739
00:31:22,730 --> 00:31:24,329
If it hadn't been for the Fourth Prince,

740
00:31:24,369 --> 00:31:25,569
I would have killed her.

741
00:31:25,609 --> 00:31:26,809
Right.

742
00:31:26,809 --> 00:31:27,930
Please simmer down.

743
00:31:28,529 --> 00:31:30,369
We can't do anything about her

744
00:31:30,529 --> 00:31:33,650
because the Fourth Prince
likes her sister.

745
00:31:34,049 --> 00:31:35,329
Stop saying the obvious.

746
00:31:37,849 --> 00:31:38,730
But Young Lord,

747
00:31:39,170 --> 00:31:42,049
I think that lady with the hairpin

748
00:31:42,450 --> 00:31:45,170
wants to approach you.

749
00:31:46,609 --> 00:31:47,329
Approach me?

750
00:31:47,730 --> 00:31:48,450
Really?

751
00:31:48,730 --> 00:31:49,730
Think about it.

752
00:31:49,809 --> 00:31:51,970
She's just an ordinary girl

753
00:31:52,170 --> 00:31:54,170
who's bound to enter the palace one day.

754
00:31:54,410 --> 00:31:57,129
If she doesn't have anyone to count on,

755
00:31:57,170 --> 00:31:59,970
she will be bullied
once she enters the palace.

756
00:32:00,329 --> 00:32:03,569
I bet she wants to
make friends with you.

757
00:32:04,329 --> 00:32:06,210
If you seize the opportunity

758
00:32:06,650 --> 00:32:09,849
and become the patron
of the future concubine of His Majesty,

759
00:32:10,170 --> 00:32:12,690
with a little sweet talk of hers,

760
00:32:13,010 --> 00:32:15,010
you'll become the second most

761
00:32:15,089 --> 00:32:16,730
respected person.

762
00:32:17,930 --> 00:32:18,569
You...

763
00:32:18,970 --> 00:32:19,609
I...

764
00:32:19,650 --> 00:32:21,890
I am enlightened, Mr. Li.

765
00:32:23,890 --> 00:32:26,609
You're so brave,
intelligent, and talented.

766
00:32:26,690 --> 00:32:28,049
I truly admire you.

767
00:32:28,170 --> 00:32:28,849
Okay.

768
00:32:29,450 --> 00:32:31,129
Let's do this.

769
00:32:31,769 --> 00:32:33,369
So enlightened.

770
00:32:42,289 --> 00:32:43,250
Jinrong.

771
00:32:44,129 --> 00:32:45,490
Once I'm gone,

772
00:32:46,289 --> 00:32:48,490
take good care of Mother.

773
00:32:49,329 --> 00:32:51,329
The whole family will count on you.

774
00:32:52,529 --> 00:32:54,250
Rest assured, Peilan.

775
00:32:55,609 --> 00:32:56,569
Jinrong.

776
00:32:57,930 --> 00:32:59,329
I could tell at first sight

777
00:32:59,369 --> 00:33:01,089
that the purse on the beam was yours.

778
00:33:01,730 --> 00:33:03,369
But I still gave it to Mother.

779
00:33:03,809 --> 00:33:04,970
Jinrong, I'm sorry.

780
00:33:07,529 --> 00:33:09,089
Cherish the last moment.

781
00:33:09,609 --> 00:33:11,049
Forget about it.

782
00:33:12,730 --> 00:33:13,569
Jinrong.

783
00:33:15,329 --> 00:33:17,970
I made this purse for you

784
00:33:19,010 --> 00:33:20,650
and haven't given it to you.

785
00:33:21,849 --> 00:33:22,849
My dear sister,

786
00:33:23,089 --> 00:33:24,369
please forgive me.

787
00:33:29,329 --> 00:33:30,329
Banxia.

788
00:33:31,609 --> 00:33:32,730
Once I'm gone,

789
00:33:33,010 --> 00:33:34,930
take good care of Mother.

790
00:33:35,609 --> 00:33:37,609
The whole family will count on you.

791
00:33:38,450 --> 00:33:39,410
Rest assured, Peilan.

792
00:33:39,609 --> 00:33:40,450
I won't feed them

793
00:33:40,529 --> 00:33:41,690
random things like you.

794
00:33:43,809 --> 00:33:46,049
I'm so sorry.

795
00:33:46,609 --> 00:33:49,369
I won't eat random things
if I have a next life.

796
00:33:50,329 --> 00:33:52,210
It's too late to regret it.

797
00:33:52,490 --> 00:33:54,089
You shouldn't have done so.

798
00:33:54,129 --> 00:33:56,329
Give me a break.

799
00:33:56,450 --> 00:33:58,129
I know I was wrong.

800
00:34:02,809 --> 00:34:03,609
Keling.

801
00:34:04,210 --> 00:34:07,250
Once I'm gone, take good care of Mother.

802
00:34:08,129 --> 00:34:10,089
The whole family will count on you.

803
00:34:10,569 --> 00:34:11,689
Got it.

804
00:34:12,169 --> 00:34:12,890
Keling.

805
00:34:14,209 --> 00:34:15,930
Peilan, let's talk tomorrow.

806
00:34:15,970 --> 00:34:17,249
There's tomorrow for you,

807
00:34:17,649 --> 00:34:19,129
but not for me.

808
00:34:19,410 --> 00:34:21,129
Can't you keep me company?

809
00:34:22,569 --> 00:34:23,569
Don't worry, Peilan.

810
00:34:23,609 --> 00:34:25,410
You'll reincarnate and come back.

811
00:34:25,649 --> 00:34:26,209
See you.

812
00:34:27,129 --> 00:34:29,529
Keling.

813
00:34:29,890 --> 00:34:31,890
Be careful when you climb over the wall.

814
00:34:32,569 --> 00:34:34,609
Who's going to
patch your clothes once I'm gone?

815
00:34:36,569 --> 00:34:37,490
Master.

816
00:34:38,450 --> 00:34:41,049
Would you like to
say something to my father?

817
00:34:41,370 --> 00:34:42,890
I can be your messenger.

818
00:34:44,169 --> 00:34:45,209
Senior.

819
00:34:46,010 --> 00:34:47,490
Never mind, Master.

820
00:34:48,370 --> 00:34:49,370
Tell him yourself

821
00:34:49,450 --> 00:34:50,810
when you eventually see him.

822
00:34:50,970 --> 00:34:53,169
I'm running out of time.

823
00:34:53,410 --> 00:34:54,450
Peilan.

824
00:34:55,529 --> 00:34:56,930
Mother.

825
00:34:57,450 --> 00:34:58,810
Trust me.

826
00:34:59,169 --> 00:35:00,169
Once I'm there,

827
00:35:00,169 --> 00:35:02,490
I'll take care of Father.

828
00:35:05,010 --> 00:35:08,209
Like father, like daughter.

829
00:35:08,249 --> 00:35:10,209
You both died from poison.

830
00:35:12,330 --> 00:35:13,490
Mother.

831
00:35:14,609 --> 00:35:15,890
Once I'm gone,

832
00:35:16,490 --> 00:35:18,609
take good care of yourself.

833
00:35:19,290 --> 00:35:20,890
Don't get mad all the time.

834
00:35:21,330 --> 00:35:23,450
Father and I will protect you.

835
00:35:24,490 --> 00:35:26,770
I know. I will.

836
00:35:26,810 --> 00:35:28,569
Rest assured.

837
00:35:29,850 --> 00:35:31,529
Mother.

838
00:35:32,850 --> 00:35:34,330
I have some money hidden up.

839
00:35:34,649 --> 00:35:36,529
It's under the rice jar in the kitchen.

840
00:35:36,569 --> 00:35:38,049
In the blue bag.

841
00:35:38,370 --> 00:35:40,010
I don't get to spend it.

842
00:35:40,290 --> 00:35:42,410
Take the money.

843
00:35:43,609 --> 00:35:46,410
What a sweet, sweet girl.

844
00:35:47,010 --> 00:35:48,490
Thank you, Mother.

845
00:36:01,290 --> 00:36:03,290
Mr. Lu.

846
00:36:05,129 --> 00:36:06,490
It's all my fault.

847
00:36:10,729 --> 00:36:12,890
I didn't know you'd die

848
00:36:14,249 --> 00:36:16,850
at such a young age.

849
00:36:20,129 --> 00:36:22,169
It's okay, Mr. Lu.

850
00:36:24,010 --> 00:36:26,209
I'm going to keep you company soon.

851
00:36:27,049 --> 00:36:28,049
No rush.

852
00:36:29,410 --> 00:36:30,410
In the next life,

853
00:36:31,049 --> 00:36:33,209
you can be Chun Peilan

854
00:36:34,010 --> 00:36:35,290
and I'll be Lu Buping.

855
00:36:36,569 --> 00:36:38,569
Then I can protect you.

856
00:36:40,569 --> 00:36:44,089
I won't feed you random things again.

857
00:36:48,049 --> 00:36:49,970
It's all my fault.

858
00:36:56,609 --> 00:36:58,290
My dearest kitchen.

859
00:36:58,890 --> 00:37:00,290
